Author: fishonthesun
Text: I'm so sorry that you're struggling so badly. When I was 14 I was sexually abused and between 15-16 I went through a period of time experiencing gender dysmorphia. For a while I identified as a agender and I was lucky enough that I hadn't developed large breasts. I cant imagine what it would be like to know that if you're unhealthy physically, getting healthy again might make you mentally unhealthy.  I hope your test results come back and are good news, wishing you the best
